<paragraph blockId="7.[491,1508,1606,1906]" pageId="7" pageNumber="752">
It was described by Haitlinger in 1986 and redescribed by Haitlinger &amp; Sundic (2015). We checked the 
<typeStatus box="[630,723,1640,1664]" pageId="7" pageNumber="752">holotype</typeStatus>
and present amended data in the redescription here.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
