<paragraph blockId="7.[491,1508,1606,1906]" box="[491,575,1778,1802]" pageId="7" pageNumber="752">Cx– 1B.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[491,1508,1606,1906]" box="[491,1323,1813,1838]" pageId="7" pageNumber="752">Leg ΙΙΙ: Ta– 1ζ, 20B; Ti–13B; Ge– 1σ, 9B; TFe– 5B; BFe– 4B; Tr– 2B; Cx– 1B.</paragraph>
